OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLow cloud retreating to North
OL,6,FSea coasts, lingering throughout the
OL,7,Fday. Sunny spells elsewhere, but
OL,8,Fisolated showers may develop across
OL,9,Fthe south into the afternoon with the
OL,10,Flow risk of these being thundery. Hot
OL,11,Fin the southwest, cooler further
OL,12,Fnortheast.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers in the south easing
OL,15,Fthis evening, but thickening cloud in
OL,16,Fthe north and northeast could bring
OL,17,Flight showers later in the night. Less
OL,18,Fwarm than previous nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
