OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FLargely fine with bright or
OL,6,Fsunny spells, most prolonged in the
OL,7,Ffar west. Cloud spreading southwards
OL,8,Fcould bring isolated showers that may
OL,9,Fturn thundery. Breezy along eastern
OL,10,Fcoasts. Less hot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
